    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to pass this beauty along to a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s in truly flawless shape, inside and out, and drives like a total dream. You really won't find one better cared for! Feel free to reach out if you want to come see this gem in person\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
