    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are firm with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct factory-new scent. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained exclusively at authorized service centers with a complete, folder-bound service history. Every electronic component, switch, and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand for a seamless transition to its next caretaker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
